表格客户管理的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('CustomerInfo')
and type = 'U')
drop table CustomerInfo
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: CustomerInfo */
/*==============================================================*/
create table CustomerInfo (
ID int identity(1,1),
CustomerNo varchar(12) not null,
CustomerName varchar(200) not null,
LinkMan varchar(12) not null,
Bank varchar(200) null,
Account varchar(20) null,
Tel varchar(50) null,
Fax varchar(50) null,
WebSite varchar(200) null,
EMail varchar(200) null,
OfficeAddr varchar(200) null,
WareHouse varchar(200) not null,
BalanceKind varchar(20) not null,
Remark varchar(200) null,
constraint PK_CLIENTINFO primary key ()
WITH (IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF) ON [PRIMARY]
)
ON [PRIMARY]
END
go
